			"content": {
				"number": 5,
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"39613\"></a>Incidenssiffror från en finländsk undersökning av agens vid lunginflammation hos barn (incidens/1&nbsp;000 barn/år) (19,20)",
				"id": "m2_145",
				"text": "<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Agens</strong></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>Ålder </strong></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><strong>&lt;&nbsp;5 år</strong></div></td><td><p><strong><div class=\"tableLine\">Ålder <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\">5–15 år</div></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Pneumokocker<a class=\"tableFootnoteLink\" href=\"#fnote_17\"><sup>a</sup></a></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">8,6</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">5,4</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Mykoplasma<sup>a</sup></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,7</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">6,6</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Klamydia<sup>a</sup></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">1,7</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">3,9</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Virus</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">8,7</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">0,7</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Okänt</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">14</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">3,7</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Total incidens</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">36</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">16</span></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_17\">a. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\">Innefattar blandinfektioner med andra bakterier och virus. </div><div class=\"tableLine\">Bakterier som fanns hos &lt;&nbsp;4&#37; av patienterna har inte ta-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">gits med. </div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
			},
